# Scan Backup Manager does not currently read any environment variables --
# all runtime configuration (admin password, language, theme, per-project
# polling interval, mapfile column mapping, etc.) is stored in the SQLite
# database and edited from the app's "Cấu hình / Cài đặt" screens.
#
# This file is kept as a placeholder for the standard project layout and so
# that `.env` stays git-ignored from day one, in case environment-based
# configuration (e.g. a shared network DB path, a notification webhook) is
# added later.
